www.reuters.com/world/china/china-india-should-maintain-momentum-high-level-talks-chinese-vice-president-2024-12-18/</guid></item><item><title>据《华尔街日报》报道，美国考虑出于国家安全考虑禁止中国TP-Link</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-considers-ban-chinas-tp-link-wsj-reports-2024-12-18/</link><description>《华尔街日报》周三援引知情人士的话报道称，在中国 TP-Link 技术公司的家用互联网路由器与网络攻击有关后，美国当局正在考虑以潜在的国家安全问题为由对其实施禁令。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 10:22:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-considers-ban-chinas-tp-link-wsj-reports-2024-12-18/</guid></item><item><title>丹麦警告称，由于俄罗斯的侵略，北极军事对抗的风险增加</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/denmark-warns-increased-risk-arctic-military-confrontation-due-russias-2024-12-18/</link><description>负责监管格陵兰岛及其周边地区安全的丹麦周三警告说，由于俄罗斯的侵略性威胁行为，北极地区发生军事对抗的风险加大。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 09:31:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/denmark-warns-increased-risk-arctic-military-confrontation-due-russias-2024-12-18/</guid></item><item><title>AMEC从美国“中国军工公司”名单中除名后股价上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/shares-amec-jump-after-removal-uss-china-military-company-list-2024-12-18/</link><description>中国领先的芯片设备制造商之一的先进微制造设备公司(AMEC)的股价周三上涨4.35%，此前该公司被从五角大楼称涉嫌与北京军方合作的中国公司名单中删除。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 07:28:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/shares-amec-jump-after-removal-uss-china-military-company-list-2024-12-18/</guid></item><item><title>致员工的信显示，特斯拉中国工厂负责人宋钢离职</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-china-factory-head-song-gang-leaves-company-letter-staff-shows-2024-12-18/</link><description>特斯拉上海工厂经理宋钢周三发给员工的一封信显示，他已经离开公司。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 07:15:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-china-factory-head-song-gang-leaves-company-letter-staff-shows-2024-12-18/</guid></item><item><title>美国特使表示，特朗普应积极参与联合国人权机构以对抗中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-should-be-active-un-rights-body-counter-china-us-envoy-says-2024-12-18/</link><description>一位美国特使告诉路透社，美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的团队应该在联合国人权理事会保持活跃，部分原因是为了对抗她所说的中国的“危险”影响力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 06:07:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-should-be-active-un-rights-body-counter-china-us-envoy-says-2024-12-18/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，伊朗革命卫队扩大了对德黑兰石油出口的控制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/irans-revolutionary-guards-extend-control-over-tehrans-oil-exports-sources-say-2024-12-18/</link><description>石油行业的各个方面都受到警卫队越来越大的影响，从秘密运输受制裁原油的油轮“影子舰队”，到物流和主要向中国出售石油的幌子公司。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 06:05:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/irans-revolutionary-guards-extend-control-over-tehrans-oil-exports-sources-say-2024-12-18/</guid></item><item><title>喷气机队何成成为首位签下职业合同的中国出生球员</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/nhl/jets-he-becomes-first-chinese-born-player-sign-pro-contract-2024-12-18/</link><description>周二，何凯文与温尼伯喷气机队签订了一份为期三年的入门级合同，成为第一位与 NHL 球队签订职业合同的中国出生球员。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 05:59:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/nhl/jets-he-becomes-first-chinese-born-player-sign-pro-contract-2024-12-18/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲对冲基金着眼于2025年中国科技领先的人工智能冲锋</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/asia-hedge-funds-eye-chinese-tech-leading-ai-charge-2025-2024-12-18/</link><description>尽管美国可能会在明年实施进一步的限制措施，但一些亚洲对冲基金仍押注于小米和百度等领先的中国科技公司，这些公司受到人工智能创新的提振。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 05:51:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/asia-hedge-funds-eye-chinese-tech-leading-ai-charge-2025-2024-12-18/</guid></item><item><title>美元在美联储面前坚挺，汽车制造商因本田-日产谈判而上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-12-18/</link><description>全球股市和美元周三小幅上涨，因投资者在今年最后一次央行会议倒计时中对投资组合进行了最后一刻的调整，而日产与本田潜在合作的消息提振了汽车股。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 03:03:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-12-18/</guid></item><item><title>越南举办军火展寻求促进国内国防工业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/vietnam-seeks-boost-domestic-defence-industry-it-hosts-arms-fair-2024-12-18/</link><description>越南将于周四在河内举行的国际军火博览会上展示本地制造的武器，以寻求发展国内工业并可能出口军事装备。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 02:58:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/vietnam-seeks-boost-domestic-defence-industry-it-hosts-arms-fair-2024-12-18/</guid></item><item><title>韩国将制定路线图以防特朗普重启朝鲜核谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-says-martial-law-attempt-undercut-political-momentum-with-trump-2024-12-18/</link><description>韩国外交部长周三表示，他正在制定一份路线图，为美国候任总统唐纳德·特朗普可能与朝鲜重启核谈判做准备，他承认首尔的政治动荡扰乱了与特朗普团队的关系。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 02:40:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-says-martial-law-attempt-undercut-political-momentum-with-trump-2024-12-18/</guid></item></channel></rss>